Requirements
Present your project proposal in a video that includes follows:
a. The system idea/ concept:
  • Synopsis and general idea about the proposed topic/system
  • System objectives and/or purpose, what the user can achieve/do in the system
  • How to use the system
  • Reporting, what is the report/output that will be generated in the system.
b. How your project will fullfil the project specifications:
  •  Array of objects (static or dynamic)
  • Encapsulation
  • Association: aggregation and composition
  • Inheritance and polymorphism
  • Exception handling
